summary: Choose your companions according to your meetings and change them at will. Maximum 4 companions, associated to hot keys F1 to F4, for to teleport you and defend you.
descriptionHtml:
[heading][color=#C0C0C0] Choose your companions according to your meetings and change them at will.
Maximum 4 companions, associated to hot keys F1 to F4, for to teleport you and defend you. [/color]

[color=#808080]Choisissez vos compagnons selon vos rencontres et changez les à volonté.
Maximum 4 compagnons associés aux raccourcis clavier F1 à F4, pour vous téléporter et vous défendre. [/color]

[color=#ffe87c]For more:[/color]

[/list][/heading]
